Subject: drm/pl111: Use drm_gem_fb_create() and drm_gem_fb_prepare_fb()
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: b6eb01a9c624b3be43c8d10c4e85e1fea935d1e3
Patch-mainline: v4.14-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

drm_fb_cma_create() and drm_fb_cma_prepare_fb() are just wrappers now,
use drm_gem_fb_create() and drm_gem_fb_prepare_fb() directly.

